HEADWORD: maple-leaf begonia
<hw>maple-leaf begonia</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
tuberous or semi-tuberous South African begonia (<spn>Begonia
dregei</spn>) having shallowly lobed ovate leaves and small white
flowers.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> grape-leaf begonia.</syn>⟦br⟧
